cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as semantic segmentation and depth estimation using deep convolutional networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves the use of contextual relationships and interactions, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of fully connected CRF, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
